argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Apollo, for its part, also recently solidified =
its leadership team
for the long haul, which was especially relevant in the wake of <strong>Mar=
c Rowan</strong>=E2=80=99s short-lived and fantastical dalliance as a candi=
date to be Trump=E2=80=99s <em>new</em> treasury secretary. <span style=3D"=
word-break:break-word;background-color:transparent;">Indeed, Marc=E2=80=99s=
 not going anywhere. Apollo has agreed to extend his contract as C.E.O. for=
 another five years, when he will be around 67 years old and Trump will be =
out of the White House. That doesn=E2=80=99t necessarily mean Marc is out o=
f the
running for the Treasury post if, say, </span><strong style=3D"background-c=
olor:transparent;">Scott Bessent</strong><span style=3D"word-break:break-wo=
rd;background-color:transparent;">, who got the job, wants out for some rea=
son or is cut down by Trump. Rowan has been the C.E.O. of Apollo since Marc=
h 2021, when founder </span><strong style=3D"background-color:transparent;"=
>Leon Black </strong><span style=3D"word-break:break-word;background-color:=
transparent;">took his leave in the wake of back-to-back
</span><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQ=
Ut2UktxclJLZ0dVa09QWTR2NnBxMzhTcDJ2djZhRT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5l=
d3MvbGVvbi1ibGFjay1pcy1iYWNrLz91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249RHJ5K1Bvd2RlcistK1NVQlNDUkl=
CRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMiUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9RHJ5K1Bvd2RlcistK1NVQl=
NDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMiUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cd=
